---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Team Building Pottery Painting"
  description="Corporate team building through creative pottery painting in Centerville, TN. Build stronger teams through collaborative creative experiences."
  price="$18-28 per person"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="team building pottery, corporate pottery painting, team bonding, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Team Building Pottery Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Looking for unique corporate team building? Bring your team together for a creative pottery painting experience that builds camaraderie, encourages collaboration, and creates lasting memories. This hands-on activity helps teams connect outside the usual office environment.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>This is team building through creativity. Your team will select pottery pieces and paint them together in a relaxed, professional atmosphere. Whether you're looking to strengthen existing bonds or help new team members connect, pottery painting offers a perfect balance of individual creativity and group interaction.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pottery pieces for each team member</li>
      <li>All painting supplies, brushes, and paints</li>
      <li>Expert guidance and facilitation</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Team-focused atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home pieces as team bonding mementos</li>
      <li>Optional: Group photos and refreshments</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Corporate team building events</li>
      <li>Department outings and bonding</li>
      <li>New employee integration</li>
      <li>Sales team celebrations</li>
      <li>Remote teams meeting in person</li>
      <li>Professional development activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and team introductions (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Each person selects their pottery piece (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Collaborative painting with team interaction (60-75 minutes)</li>
      <li>Sharing and team photos (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Team members take home their pieces</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $18-28 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 5-30 team members (larger groups available)<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> No experience required
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your team building pottery painting!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect team building activity! Our team connected in ways we never do in the office. Everyone loved it and we saw real bonding happen."</em></p>
      <p><strong>Mark, HR Manager</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"We've done many team building activities, but this was by far the most engaging. Great balance of creativity and team interaction."</em></p>
      <p><strong>Jennifer, Operations Director</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Our sales team needed something different for our quarterly outing. This was memorable, fun, and brought us closer together!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>David, Sales Manager</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
